{
  "doc_id": "FC-LS",
  "source_pdf": "/Users/zwy/毕设/V7/data/raw/FC-LS.pdf",
  "page": 199,
  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0002",
      "text": " 180",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0003",
      "text": "The Nx_Port originating the PRLI request shall not consider the image pair to be established until it",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.95,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0004",
      "text": "has taken the necessary action to establish the image pair, and has received an LS_ACC reply Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        540.01,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0005",
      "text": "quence indicating that the image pair has been established.  The Nx_Port responding to the PRLI re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        539.86,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0006",
      "text": "quest does not consider the image pair to be established until the necessary action is taken at the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        93.65,
        539.98,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0007",
      "text": "Nx_Port to establish the image pair, and an LS_ACC reply Sequence is sent.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        105.64,
        435.92,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0008",
      "text": "If a link error is detected when a PRLI request is received, the appropriate response, if any, is made,",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        540.09,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0009",
      "text": "and the image pair is not established.  If the recipient Nx_Port is not logged in with the requesting",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        142.96,
        539.95,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0010",
      "text": "port it shall reply with a LOGO ELS Sequence, or with an LS_RJT ELS Sequence with a reason code",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        539.96,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0011",
      "text": "of \"Unable to perform command request\" and a reason code explanation of \"N_Port Login required\".",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        540.02,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0012",
      "text": "If an LS_RJT is sent in response to a PRLI request for an image pair that is already established, the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        539.99,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0013",
      "text": "existing image pair is unaffected.  If an LS_RJT, P_BSY, F_BSY, P_RJT, or F_RJT response is re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        539.96,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0014",
      "text": "ceived to a PRLI request, the PRLI request may be retried until the image pair is established.  The",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        540.01,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0015",
      "text": "number of retries is system dependent.  In the case of LS_RJT, whether or not the PRLI is retried de-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        539.97,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0016",
      "text": "pends on the LS_RJT reason code.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        253.2,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0017",
      "text": "In the event that there is an error in the response to establish an image pair, the originating Nx_Port",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        540.01,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0018",
      "text": "shall not assume that the requested action has or has not taken place. If the Nx_Port that originates",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.02,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0019",
      "text": "a PRLI request receives no valid response, the Nx_Port should retry the request.  The number of re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        539.94,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0020",
      "text": "tries is system dependent.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        212.08,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0021",
      "text": "7.1.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        118.22,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0022",
      "text": "PRLI/PRLO Relationships",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        310.96,
        249.86,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0023",
      "text": "7.1.2.1  Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        190.41,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0024",
      "text": "Process_Associator (PA) images may exist in the following relationships.  Any of these relationships",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        358.96,
        540.09,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0025",
      "text": "may be established as a default condition using mechanisms not specified by this standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.96,
        499.87,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0026",
      "text": "7.1.2.2  PA not supported",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.96,
        215.97,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0027",
      "text": "If one or both of the Originator and Responder do not support PAs, no valid PA is specified in any",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        540.0,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0028",
      "text": "frame of any exchange.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        200.43,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0029",
      "text": "The PRLI/PRLO should allow control over the enabling and disabling the specified services for the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        540.0,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0030",
      "text": "entire Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        162.65,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0031",
      "text": "7.1.2.3  PA required by originator, supported by responder",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        373.17,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0032",
      "text": "If the Originator requires PAs, the Originator is expected to communicate only when a valid PA is in-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        540.1,
        526.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0033",
      "text": "cluded in the initial Association_Header.  The Responder provides a final Association_Header and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        539.92,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0034",
      "text": "provides other Association_Headers as required.  The PA establishes a routing to a particular Origi-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        539.94,
        550.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0035",
      "text": "nator process (or group of related processes).  There is no relationship between PAs identified",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        539.97,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0036",
      "text": "through one Nx_Port of a host system and another Nx_Port from the same host.  The PA may addi-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        540.1,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0037",
      "text": "tionally be used by the FC-4 in a FC-4 dependent manner.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        353.79,
        586.07
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0038",
      "text": "The PRLI request pages have valid Originator PA values and invalid Responder PA values.  This",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        540.04,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0039",
      "text": "PRLI informs the Responder of the Originator requirements and capabilities for each TYPE of FC-4.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        535.9,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0040",
      "text": "The PRLI and PRLO may allow control over the enabling and disabling the access of each Originator",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        635.02,
        540.08,
        646.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0041",
      "text": "Process to the Responder Nx_Port.  Communication with image pairs that have not been established",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        647.02,
        540.01,
        658.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p199_s0042",
      "text": "is not allowed, even if both PAs exist and have the proper requirements and capabilities.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        659.02,
        485.87,
        670.13
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    }
  ],
  "asset_ids": []
}